#: ../channels/microsoft365/accounts/account-setup.rst:169
msgid ""
"This is a Microsoft 365 specific issue which you have to solve with "
"Microsoft. However, you can have a look at `Microsofts documentation "
"<https://docs.microsoft.com/en-us/exchange/recipients-in-exchange-online/"
"manage-user-mailboxes/change-deleted-item-retention>`_ which might allow you "
"to solve the issue on your own."
msgstr ""
"Este é um problema específico do Microsoft 365 que você precisa resolver com "
"a Microsoft. No entanto, você pode consultar a `documentação da Microsoft "
"<https://docs.microsoft.com/en-us/exchange/recipients-in-exchange-online/"
"manage-user-mailboxes/change-deleted-item-retention>`_, que pode permitir "
"que você resolva o problema por conta própria."

#: ../channels/microsoft365/accounts/account-setup.rst:174
msgid ""
"As soon as the issue has been fixed, the Zammad channel will recover "
"automatically."
msgstr ""
"Assim que o problema for corrigido, o canal do Zammad se recuperará "
"automaticamente."

#: ../channels/microsoft365/accounts/account-setup.rst:177
msgid ""
"Have a look at the :doc:`common errors section <../common-errors>` if you "
"still face issues with your M365 account."
msgstr ""
