"This field is only displayed for *pre-defined webhooks*! It only serves as a "
"reference to a pre-defined webhook. It is not possible to change it for "
"existing webhooks. Depending on the pre-defined webhook type, additional "
"fields may be rendered below this one. They can be used for additional "
