#: ../manage/webhook/examples/generic-notifications-trigger.rst:61
msgid ""
"Select ticket **Escalation at** attribute and set the operator to *has "
"reached warning*."
msgstr ""
"Selecione o atributo **Escalation at** do ticket e defina o operador como "
"*has reached warning*."

#: ../manage/webhook/examples/generic-notifications-trigger.rst:64
msgid ""
