#: ../settings/security/third-party/openid-connect.rst:2
msgid "OpenID Connect"
msgstr "OpenID Connect"

#: ../settings/security/third-party/openid-connect.rst:4
msgid ""
"OpenID is an easy and safe way for people to reuse an existing account and "
"user profile from an OpenID provider. Connect your OpenID provider (OP) as a "
"single sign-on (SSO) method."
msgstr ""
"O OpenID é uma forma fácil e segura de as pessoas reutilizarem uma conta e "
"um perfil de usuário existentes de um provedor OpenID. Conecte seu provedor "
"OpenID (OP) como um método de logon único (SSO)."

#: ../settings/security/third-party/openid-connect.rst:8
msgid ""
"The relying party (RP) is Zammad and the OpenID provider is a software "
"service that you either host or subscribe to (e.g. `Keycloak <https://"
"www.keycloak.org/>`_)."
msgstr ""
"A parte confiante (RP) é o Zammad, e o provedor OpenID é um serviço de "
"software que você hospeda ou assina (por exemplo, `Keycloak <https://"
"www.keycloak.org/>`_)."

#: ../settings/security/third-party/openid-connect.rst:13
msgid ""
"This guide assumes you are already using OpenID Connect within your "
"organization (i.e. that your OP is fully set up)."
msgstr ""
"Este guia pressupõe que você já está usando o OpenID Connect na sua "
"organização (ou seja, que seu OP está totalmente configurado)."

#: ../settings/security/third-party/openid-connect.rst:15
msgid ""
"The current implementation of OpenID Connect in Zammad requires OpenID "
"Connect Discovery to simplify the configuration."
msgstr ""
"A implementação atual do OpenID Connect no Zammad requer o OpenID Connect "
"Discovery para simplificar a configuração."

#: ../settings/security/third-party/openid-connect.rst:17
msgid ""
"The connection between Zammad and your OP has to be secure. Both systems "
"must be reachable via HTTPS. Self-signed certificates are not supported."
msgstr ""
"A conexão entre o Zammad e seu OP precisa ser segura. Ambos os sistemas "
"devem estar acessíveis via HTTPS. Certificados autoassinados não são "
"suportados."

#: ../settings/security/third-party/openid-connect.rst:20
msgid "Our instructions are based on connecting Zammad with Keycloak."
msgstr "Nossas instruções são baseadas na conexão do Zammad com o Keycloak."

#: ../settings/security/third-party/openid-connect.rst:21
msgid "PKCE is currently only supporting SHA256 as code challenge method."
msgstr "Atualmente, o PKCE suporta apenas SHA256 como método de code challenge."

